== Welcome to mombot

Mombot is a private social network designed to keep the riffraff out!  Outsiders apply, insiders vote. Simple.

Check the TODO for stuff we haven't finished.

== How to install

=== looks
* change your SMTP stuff in config/environments/production.rb -- actually, this doesn't matter. we don't send any emails.
* change public/4440-application-form.tex
* change app/views/layouts/main.erb change the link bar

=== does
* change config/database.yml to talk to your databases
* run 'RAILS_ENV=production rake db:migrate' from the root on your prod server
